```py
function bubbel_sort(sequence)
    do   
        swapped = false
        for i = 1 to length(sequence) – 2
            if sequence[i] > sequence[i+1] then
                swap(sequence[i], sequence[i+1])
		     swapped = true
            end_if
        end_for
    while swapped
    return sequence
end_function
```
